WEBVTT

00:07.083 --> 00:09.083
[pulsing music playing]

00:30.000 --> 00:32.000
♪ ♪

00:48.041 --> 00:51.290
- [horns honking]
- [indistinct shouting]

00:51.291 --> 00:52.957
[O] Express delivery, coming through.

00:52.958 --> 00:55.832
- Hey! That's my soda!
- Thank you!

00:55.833 --> 00:57.290
[exciting music playing]

00:57.291 --> 00:59.374
[Buddibot] <i>This delivery is late, O,
but you got 30 seconds</i>

00:59.375 --> 01:01.541
<i>- on the time-slide multiplier.</i>
- Watch out!

01:02.583 --> 01:03.790
I got this.

01:03.791 --> 01:05.625
- [grunts]
- [horns honking]

01:05.750 --> 01:06.958
<i>20 seconds, O.</i>

01:08.000 --> 01:09.250
Uh, hey.

01:09.375 --> 01:11.500
[Buddibot] <i>You're only 50 gems
from a secret bike upgrade.</i>

01:13.250 --> 01:15.207
[horn honks]

01:15.208 --> 01:17.041
Yikes!

01:18.166 --> 01:20.124
- [tires screech]
- Whoo!

01:20.125 --> 01:21.291
<i>Target acquired.</i>

01:22.708 --> 01:25.040
- Hey. Riding here.
- [horn honks]

01:25.041 --> 01:26.249
[tires screech]

01:26.250 --> 01:28.415
[grunts]

01:28.416 --> 01:30.207
[beeping]

01:30.208 --> 01:32.749
<i>Nine, eight...</i>

01:32.750 --> 01:34.707
- [grunts]
<i>- ...seven, six...</i>

01:34.708 --> 01:36.624
<i>...five,</i>

01:36.625 --> 01:38.540
<i>four, three,</i>

01:38.541 --> 01:40.290
<i>two, one.</i>

01:40.291 --> 01:41.707
<i>Delivered.</i>

01:41.708 --> 01:43.915
<i>- One box of paperclips.</i>
- [laughs] Whew.

01:43.916 --> 01:45.874
<i>Congratulations, O.</i>

01:45.875 --> 01:47.915
<i>Secret bike upgrade unlocked.</i>

01:47.916 --> 01:49.457
Thanks, Buddi.

01:49.458 --> 01:51.290
So, what do I get?

01:51.291 --> 01:54.999
[grunts] Gecko-tread tires?
Maybe a padded seat?

01:55.000 --> 01:57.207
<i>We're talking legendary-status swag.</i>

01:57.208 --> 02:00.374
<i>You won... burnt orange.</i>

02:00.375 --> 02:02.958
<i>Virtual paint job,
only some restrictions apply.</i>

02:04.041 --> 02:06.165
- What the--
- [horn honks]

02:06.166 --> 02:09.165
[Buddibot] <i>Did you know
that 67.2% of Buddibot users</i>

02:09.166 --> 02:10.749
<i>find virtual rewards satisfying?</i>

02:10.750 --> 02:13.749
<i>They have become
the biggest motivators in our toolbox.</i>

02:13.750 --> 02:15.749
- [sighs]
<i>- Fast delivery, great for the environment.</i>

02:15.750 --> 02:18.499
<i>And with the added value
of virtual validation?</i>

02:18.500 --> 02:19.999
<i>Priceless.</i>

02:20.000 --> 02:23.874
<i>Speaking of virtual validation,
I'm so proud of your achievement, O.</i>

02:23.875 --> 02:28.040
Yeah, because burnt orange
is so much more awesome than orange.

02:28.041 --> 02:30.790
<i>Yes, it is. And more awesomeness awaits,</i>

02:30.791 --> 02:32.707
<i>because lunch break is over.</i>

02:32.708 --> 02:34.957
[Johnny] Hey there, O.

02:34.958 --> 02:36.999
Uh, my name's Johnny. Nice to meet you.

02:37.000 --> 02:40.332
I've, uh, got a package
for you to deliver.

02:40.333 --> 02:42.415
Sorry, uh, Johnny, right?

02:42.416 --> 02:44.624
Y-You got to go through dispatch, man.

02:44.625 --> 02:46.165
I-I can't take random packages...

02:46.166 --> 02:49.249
<i>Don't trust him. This guy looks sketchy.</i>

02:49.250 --> 02:52.165
"Grimsby"? Why is that so--

02:52.166 --> 02:54.874
Trust me. Only you can deliver this.

02:54.875 --> 02:57.040
- [warbling]
- Whoa, hold on.

02:57.041 --> 02:58.207
What is this thing?

02:58.208 --> 02:59.249
A conduit.

02:59.250 --> 03:01.290
What the--? Hey!

03:01.291 --> 03:04.124
- No. No, no. Hey!
- It is the most valuable thing
in the world.

03:04.125 --> 03:06.582
Assuming you have
a great imagination, of course.

03:06.583 --> 03:08.499
Uh, is this thing real?

03:08.500 --> 03:09.832
[warbles]

03:09.833 --> 03:11.499
Ah, you're real. Wow.

03:11.500 --> 03:13.874
But you better get going
before they take it.

03:13.875 --> 03:15.249
Who?

03:15.250 --> 03:16.499
- See that?
- What's going on?

03:16.500 --> 03:17.749
- Whoa!
- [woman screams]

03:17.750 --> 03:20.249
- [Helldiver] Ma'am, I'm gonna need you
to hand over the conduit.
- Whoa!

03:20.250 --> 03:22.832
Wait, no, hold on. Trust me, I'm trying.

03:22.833 --> 03:26.457
- But it won't hand over me.
- [Helldiver] The conduit, now!

03:26.458 --> 03:27.999
[Buddibot] <i>Just give it to them, O.</i>

03:28.000 --> 03:30.582
[Helldiver] Face liberty, courier.
You can't run from freedom!

03:30.583 --> 03:32.540
[grunts]

03:32.541 --> 03:34.582
- Halt! Stop!
- Hey, hey, hey!

03:34.583 --> 03:37.000
Democracy isn't done with you, girl!

03:38.250 --> 03:42.540
Uh, Buddi, I have no idea
what's going on, but map me.

03:42.541 --> 03:44.540
12394 Grimsby.

03:44.541 --> 03:47.665
<i>This gelatinous creature
is an unauthorized passenger.</i>

03:47.666 --> 03:49.249
Oh, shit!

03:49.250 --> 03:51.040
<i>And that is an unauthorized colossus.</i>

03:51.041 --> 03:53.040
- [growls]
- [conduit chitters]

03:53.041 --> 03:54.124
- What is that?
- [exclaims]

03:54.125 --> 03:56.290
[pedestrians scream]

03:56.291 --> 03:57.707
It's following us!

03:57.708 --> 03:59.790
Oh, no, no, no. Move, move, please!

03:59.791 --> 04:03.165
<i>It must belong to these creatures.
Let them have it.</i>

04:03.166 --> 04:04.791
Buddi, we can’t just-- Whoa!

04:05.875 --> 04:08.457
Oh, God, this is amazing!

04:08.458 --> 04:10.624
<i>This is definitely
not an approved upgrade.</i>

04:10.625 --> 04:11.958
[grunts]

04:15.291 --> 04:18.541
Woo-hoo! That was insane!

04:22.666 --> 04:23.833
[roars]

04:24.916 --> 04:26.165
Seriously?

04:26.166 --> 04:27.832
- You guys want to play?
- [engine revs]

04:27.833 --> 04:29.166
Then game on.

04:33.750 --> 04:34.958
Can't touch this.

04:37.208 --> 04:38.624
- Shit.
- [Female Helldiver] Halt!

04:38.625 --> 04:42.457
- You can't run from freedom!
- [Male Helldiver] Gimme that conduit.

04:42.458 --> 04:44.040
- Any ideas?
- [conduit squeaks]

04:44.041 --> 04:46.249
[Female Helldiver] Sweet liberty.
What is that?

04:46.250 --> 04:48.790
[Male Helldiver] I don't know,
but let's shoot it.

04:48.791 --> 04:49.957
[O] Woo-hoo!

04:49.958 --> 04:51.790
Dude, you're like a wizard.

04:51.791 --> 04:54.374
Now that was off the hook.

04:54.375 --> 04:56.207
[mysterious music playing]

04:56.208 --> 04:58.999
- All right, okay, which way?
- [conduit squeaking]

04:59.000 --> 05:01.999
- Let's do it!
- [Buddibot] <i>No way.</i>

05:02.000 --> 05:04.124
Your Deliverus contract
clearly stipulates--

05:04.125 --> 05:05.874
[Male Helldiver] The conduit
or molten lead, courier.

05:05.875 --> 05:08.582
- Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
- [Female Helldiver] Democracy
isn't done with you!

05:08.583 --> 05:11.915
- [Buddibot] <i>O!</i>
- Stop. I can't see, you little bastard.

05:11.916 --> 05:14.000
<i>Exit the vehicle, now.</i>

05:16.500 --> 05:19.082
[dramatic music playing]

05:19.083 --> 05:20.457
♪ ♪

05:20.458 --> 05:23.374
- [O screams]
<i>- Cease and desist right now.</i>

05:23.375 --> 05:27.290
<i>If you do not do it,
I am taking away burnt orange.</i>

05:27.291 --> 05:29.707
It's just orange!

05:29.708 --> 05:31.750
<i>No!</i>

05:37.083 --> 05:38.750
[inhales sharply]

05:40.041 --> 05:41.708
[giggles]

05:43.125 --> 05:47.041
Whoo! We are next level now!

05:48.250 --> 05:50.665
<i>This is zero-gem behavior, O.</i>

05:50.666 --> 05:53.540
You know what, Buddi?
Screw you and your stupid little gems

05:53.541 --> 05:55.208
because I quit!

05:56.791 --> 05:58.290
[horns honking]

05:58.291 --> 06:00.165
<i>- You can't quit ever.</i>
- [conduit squeaks]

06:00.166 --> 06:01.624
<i>- You must keep playing.</i>
- [grunts]

06:01.625 --> 06:05.041
Buddi, get off of me,
you creepy little robot.

06:06.458 --> 06:08.958
[Buddibot grunting]

06:12.000 --> 06:14.582
[O whooping]

06:14.583 --> 06:17.458
Okay, hold on, okay?
I'm gonna get you home.

06:18.958 --> 06:23.791
<i>Well, someone didn't read
their Buddibot user agreement carefully.</i>

06:26.166 --> 06:29.958
[deep voice] <i>I don't play games.
I win them.</i>

06:31.041 --> 06:32.207
<i>You're the main character.</i>

06:32.208 --> 06:33.540
- [growls]
- [exclaims]

06:33.541 --> 06:35.041
[screaming]

06:37.083 --> 06:39.541
[panicked chatter]

06:40.500 --> 06:42.041
[conduit chitters]

06:47.666 --> 06:48.541
Shit!

06:50.958 --> 06:52.625
[screams, grunts]

06:55.708 --> 06:58.249
[exciting music playing]

06:58.250 --> 07:00.290
♪ ♪

07:00.291 --> 07:02.166
[grunting]

07:04.583 --> 07:06.915
[Buddibot] <i>Game over, O.</i>

07:06.916 --> 07:08.665
[straining]

07:08.666 --> 07:10.124
<i>You lose.</i>

07:10.125 --> 07:11.708
[screaming]

07:18.000 --> 07:20.000
[wind whistling]

07:21.291 --> 07:23.541
[gasps, grunts]

07:25.583 --> 07:27.791
[screaming]

07:29.041 --> 07:31.332
[grunting]

07:31.333 --> 07:33.958
[chittering]

07:37.458 --> 07:38.958
[O screams]

07:48.666 --> 07:49.707
[chitters]

07:49.708 --> 07:52.208
[O] Oh, look. Grimsby.

07:54.000 --> 07:56.749
[Buddibot] <i>I-I've... reset your account.</i>

07:56.750 --> 07:58.832
<i>Please re-enter your password...</i>

07:58.833 --> 08:00.790
<i>P-P-Password.</i>

08:00.791 --> 08:03.207
[O] What a sore loser.

08:03.208 --> 08:05.332
[siren wailing in distance]

08:05.333 --> 08:07.207
[atmospheric music playing]

08:07.208 --> 08:08.915
♪ ♪

08:08.916 --> 08:12.458
Hello? Anybody home?

08:17.000 --> 08:19.665
[O's Mother] <i>Everyone, grab a controller.</i>

08:19.666 --> 08:22.832
- [kids clamoring and laughing]
- [controllers clicking]

08:22.833 --> 08:24.707
[Young O] <i>Mom, Mom, we beat it.</i>

08:24.708 --> 08:26.499
[O's Mother] <i>All right, O,
time for dinner.</i>

08:26.500 --> 08:27.707
[Young O] <i>Coming!</i>

08:27.708 --> 08:30.082
<i>- One more minute, Mom.</i>
- [O's Mother] <i>Ah, just one more round.</i>

08:30.083 --> 08:32.041
[Young O] <i>This next level is crazy.</i>

08:32.166 --> 08:34.124
The Source.

08:34.125 --> 08:36.791
Right. I get it now.

08:36.916 --> 08:39.082
[conduit warbles]

08:39.083 --> 08:41.082
[chitters]

08:41.083 --> 08:42.916
[hinge creaks]

08:44.958 --> 08:46.415
Whoa!

08:46.416 --> 08:48.790
[soaring music playing]

08:48.791 --> 08:50.624
♪ ♪

08:50.625 --> 08:52.874
I remember.

08:52.875 --> 08:56.707
The world used
to feel like this every day.

08:56.708 --> 08:58.416
[bike chirps]

08:59.875 --> 09:03.040
- [laughs] Yo, that was fun, though.
- I told you she'd be good.

09:03.041 --> 09:04.499
[Johnny] Hey.

09:04.500 --> 09:06.790
Nice bike, O. Love the color.

09:06.791 --> 09:09.958
But... you know,
it might look better in burnt orange.

09:11.041 --> 09:13.624
So, what was this all about?

09:13.625 --> 09:17.332
Just a little game we like to play.
Kind of a test, really.

09:17.333 --> 09:18.957
And I totally passed.

09:18.958 --> 09:22.207
So... best two out of three?

09:22.208 --> 09:24.957
You know what? Why not?

09:24.958 --> 09:27.082
[adventurous music playing]

09:27.083 --> 09:28.750
♪ ♪

09:34.708 --> 09:36.083
[giggles]

09:38.166 --> 09:40.166
[upbeat music playing]

10:09.833 --> 10:11.833
♪ ♪

10:39.000 --> 10:41.000
♪ ♪
